Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.45,0:00:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓抑高昂的鼓動 奔向暮色昏暗的街道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.36,0:00:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心和客套之間 對那傢伙的想法複雜交錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.86,0:00:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有答案也無妨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.74,0:00:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這份愛粉身碎骨 你的表情為何如此寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.64,0:00:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謊言 心機 嫉妒 背叛 有如家常便飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.28,0:00:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無須大驚小怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.89,0:00:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玻璃之心點燃火苗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.96,0:00:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多想再去見你一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.19,0:00:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不行動 何時才要做呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.03,0:00:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇花開 薔薇花落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.00,0:00:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心中有我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.97,0:01:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高雅的 優美的 華麗的飛舞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.11,0:01:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇花開 薔薇花飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.25,0:01:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼中有你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.28,0:01:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用心祈禱的話 一定能改變命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.46,0:01:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒熱情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.56,0:01:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活得燦爛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.63,0:01:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你同在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.97,0:01:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第11話 龍的指引

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.08,0:01:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美玉，妳的生日被搞砸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.49,0:01:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎\N反正今天的事是我所樂見的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.83,0:01:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是沒想到會變成這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.46,0:01:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北斗傳人的對戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.23,0:02:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧妳讓我看到了精采場面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.96,0:02:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是拳志郎的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.06,0:02:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N而妳也一腳踏進了那個世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.17,0:02:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經做好心理準備了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.84,0:02:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之，妳先避避風頭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.31,0:02:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吳一定會來追殺妳的\N或許就是今晚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.45,0:02:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.82,0:02:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其被那個吳玷污\N我寧願選擇一死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.72,0:03:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的自尊心還是一樣很強啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.39,0:03:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我送妳一個好消息\N當生日禮物吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.43,0:03:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好消息？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.04,0:03:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，這樣應該就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.05,0:03:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是用木頭會比較輕鬆吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.85,0:03:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊\N用鐵塊固定就完全動不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.56,0:03:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.23,0:03:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.53,0:03:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過有點難看就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.67,0:03:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前在上海修行拳法時\N也都是這樣療傷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.51,0:03:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.34,0:03:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手會斷掉的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.58,0:03:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.58,0:04:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就說會痛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.65,0:04:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，至少我知道潘在哪裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.43,0:04:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒死？那個人還活着？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.36,0:04:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，妳的情人潘光琳並沒有死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.50,0:04:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人…還活着…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.84,0:04:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.75,0:04:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，他人在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.72,0:04:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不遠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.22,0:04:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈王說他兩小時前才見過潘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.56,0:04:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他打鬥時聞到了潘的氣味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.37,0:04:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能確定潘還沒死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.47,0:04:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…\N光憑你像狗的鼻子還是不够吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.88,0:05:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.15,0:05:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先，靈王身上傳出了水的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.02,0:05:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水的味道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.95,0:05:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是黃埔江那種大河的水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.52,0:05:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，那是蘇州河的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.36,0:05:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後，還有線香的味道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.23,0:05:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是墳墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.97,0:05:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吳東來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.14,0:05:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哪處墳墓是跟他有關的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.48,0:05:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墳墓？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.34,0:05:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟女星狂有關的墳墓…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.58,0:05:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女星狂…爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.32,0:05:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得之前自殺的紅星林燐夕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.42,0:05:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吳東來超迷她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.52,0:05:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對喔，吳東來的怪異性癖好\N把燐夕逼到自殺身亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.43,0:05:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果他還把自家祖墳遷到\N她的墓地旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.23,0:05:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.13,0:05:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠近蘇州河畔\N新閘附近新闢的墓地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.77,0:05:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是公肇山莊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.86,0:06:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡的確有可能用來囚禁潘老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.36,0:06:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.96,0:06:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳，爸爸，我們快去公肇山莊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.83,0:06:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.33,0:06:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.60,0:06:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不行呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.47,0:06:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊，好不容易掌握了位置耶\N為什麼不去呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.11,0:06:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不去？拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.72,0:06:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.02,0:06:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個混帳說美玉愛上老子的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.62,0:06:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您搞錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.22,0:06:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.36,0:06:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為何閻王會出現在大戲院裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.26,0:07:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太可疑了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.20,0:07:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說老子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.21,0:07:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.08,0:07:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被他們擺一道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.88,0:07:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美玉和閻王根本是同夥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.88,0:07:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們馬上去把美玉抓過來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.09,0:07:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.92,0:07:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.09,0:07:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死定了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.66,0:07:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一個好點子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.07,0:07:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒下廚做菜啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.24,0:07:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不…不會吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.64,0:07:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大要下廚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.07,0:07:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美玉難得過生日啊\N我要送上親手做的料理給她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.55,0:07:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.65,0:07:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們快去給我準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.48,0:07:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.82,0:08:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其被做成那種料理…\N還不如死了算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.43,0:08:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着瞧吧，美玉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.67,0:08:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎\N那美玉可能也會有危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.54,0:08:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N不知道吳下一步會怎麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.01,0:08:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上還有一個靈王…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.31,0:08:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道吳的動向\N我們是無法隨便出手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.65,0:08:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們到底該去哪裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.71,0:08:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要去救潘老大？\N還是去保護美玉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.99,0:08:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳，你說話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.23,0:08:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳，那是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.43,0:08:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅龍盤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.73,0:08:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是以前有一位精通\N密教占星術的道士給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.74,0:08:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他教我遇到問題時\N可以問問這條龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.58,0:08:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時，有一次我正在修練拳法…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.08,0:09:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果受了重傷，動彈不得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺子你有事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.92,0:09:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我臉上有怪東西嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.96,0:09:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看不出來，看不出來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.03,0:09:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的面相真是不可思議啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.33,0:09:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看不出來你的命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.91,0:10:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老道，我的面相有那麼慘嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.58,0:10:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，我不是這個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.75,0:10:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世間的宿命是無法任意改變的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.66,0:10:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個村子以前熱鬧富庶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.16,0:10:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻也難以抵抗宿命\N而變成這副寂寥的模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.03,0:10:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過人的命運卻可以改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.40,0:10:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要施一點小法術就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.77,0:10:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你的面相顯示出\N你的命運可以自由改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.64,0:10:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才說我看不出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.58,0:10:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個老道難不成知道\N我是北斗的傳人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.32,0:10:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你一副不知所措的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.59,0:10:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，這個你拿去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.23,0:10:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是羅龍盤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.20,0:11:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後當你不知何去何從之時\N就問問這條龍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.27,0:11:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是就是正面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否會出現反面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.91,0:11:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…\N我沒有道理接受你的饋贈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.12,0:11:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說了\N沒道理，但是有緣份啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.29,0:11:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽好，能改變命運的就是緣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.96,0:11:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要誠心祈禱就能遇到有緣人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.93,0:11:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在祈禱…\N“我想遇見北斗的傳人”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.44,0:11:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老道你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.87,0:11:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北斗的傳人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.37,0:11:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你有趟美好的命運之旅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.33,0:11:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指示去路的神奇羅龍盤啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.37,0:12:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.71,0:12:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要試試看？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.61,0:12:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.81,0:12:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也許就是道士口中\N我該向羅龍盤詢問去向的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.86,0:12:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去救潘，答案為是或否
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.87,0:13:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是正面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.31,0:13:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，去公肇山莊\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.88,0:13:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去救潘出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.05,0:13:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.79,0:13:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，你怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.26,0:13:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，前面好像有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.67,0:13:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的表情還真恐怖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.67,0:13:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳，你認識他嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.94,0:13:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的右手應該也斷了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.81,0:13:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然還有本事來這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.21,0:13:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼還笑得出來啊\N現在該怎麼辦才好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.71,0:14:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來他是不打算讓我們過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.39,0:14:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.36,0:14:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.43,0:14:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對喔，撞過去就對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.03,0:14:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.84,0:14:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想死的話就閃邊去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.04,0:14:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪，他不躲開嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.88,0:14:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想死啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.45,0:14:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾開啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.12,0:14:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手臂包得比我還粗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.79,0:14:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快撞到了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.96,0:14:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.80,0:14:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是何方神聖啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.37,0:14:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是靈王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.70,0:14:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你幹嘛不早點講啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.17,0:14:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.71,0:15:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙是想去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.21,0:15:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了，我先去解決另一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.66,0:15:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳志郎現在應該已經去救潘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.93,0:15:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作不快點\N潘可能今晚就會被殺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.37,0:15:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，為什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.24,0:15:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳只愛潘一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吳為此而心生怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.41,0:15:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此他故意不殺潘\N一直折磨他到現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.75,0:15:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.12,0:16:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像開始了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.06,0:16:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好討厭處理善後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.73,0:16:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不想看“那個”的裝盤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.07,0:16:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想早點回家喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.44,0:16:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潘，你知道今天是什麼日子嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.81,0:16:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，今天是美玉的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.18,0:16:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶生宴上必須端上最好的菜色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.79,0:16:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想替美玉做一道“龍虎鬥”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.96,0:16:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？很棒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.13,0:17:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.87,0:17:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想提醒我龍虎鬥少了虎吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.87,0:17:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算你夠細心，的確是少了一隻虎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.44,0:17:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.78,0:17:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣料理不算是完成耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.71,0:17:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，你不用操心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.32,0:17:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有現成的“虎”了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.92,0:17:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，今日的龍虎鬥的主菜\N是人稱上海之虎的潘光琳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.69,0:17:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的人頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.86,0:17:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣，龍虎鬥就算是完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.26,0:17:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想早點看到美玉毫不知情\N開心吃下去的表情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.24,0:17:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.95,0:17:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝飾得真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.98,0:17:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，開始做菜啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.22,0:18:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在笑什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.43,0:18:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在對美玉糾纏不休啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.96,0:18:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.93,0:18:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潘，這種好女人配你太浪費了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.00,0:18:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以料理上桌後\N我要去好好的疼愛她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.98,0:18:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想得美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.21,0:18:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.28,0:18:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不明白嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.72,0:18:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我來告訴你好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.88,0:18:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是臉的問題，是臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.75,0:18:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.79,0:18:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美玉只愛帥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.19,0:18:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她能正常分辨出\N哪種人才是美男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.63,0:18:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你呢？請問你是帥哥嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.77,0:18:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我比起來，你能看嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.81,0:18:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道差別了吧？\N我們之間的差別…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.98,0:18:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吳東來，你聽好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.75,0:18:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人的行為會決定他的外表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.78,0:19:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的長相反應了你的醜陋行徑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.82,0:19:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，快動手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.56,0:19:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則我都快笑死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.86,0:19:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥哥就算死了還是帥哥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.03,0:19:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你活得不耐煩啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.63,0:19:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直提什麼長相…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.44,0:19:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我把你下油鍋…很燙的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.38,0:19:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人的嫉妒真是讓人看不下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.68,0:19:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.05,0:19:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.79,0:19:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們怎麼都被下油鍋啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.46,0:19:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.63,0:19:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麵粉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.87,0:19:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,料理的時間到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.30,0:19:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主菜是炸海獅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.57,0:19:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閻王…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.05,0:20:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吳東來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.39,0:20:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無視我的警告還敢留在上海\N你一定會後悔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.56,0:20:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你口氣倒是很大嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.00,0:20:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我一槍斃了潘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.94,0:20:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣啊，閻王\N我看後悔莫及的人是你啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.21,0:20:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開槍啊，有種就殺了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.68,0:20:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我活不久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.28,0:20:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨死前能够見到拳志郎\N我死而無憾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.65,0:20:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友真是不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.02,0:20:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人動容啊，閻王\N你忍心對好朋友見死不救嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.06,0:20:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你殺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.90,0:20:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.53,0:21:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你動手沒關係\N反正接着就輪到你去死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.47,0:21:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確定？我真的會扣扳機喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.28,0:21:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快殺啊，豬頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.95,0:21:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快殺啊，豬頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.38,0:21:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扣下扳機我就死定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.25,0:21:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我不能在這裡示弱…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.82,0:21:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好，我來真的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.13,0:21:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的，真的，真的喔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.03,0:21:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一點啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.07,0:21:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，混帳，混帳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.54,0:21:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.14,0:21:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跑去哪了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.57,0:21:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可惡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.47,0:21:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管了，我先斃了潘再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.05,0:21:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小鬼是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.68,0:21:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，現在輪到我上場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.89,0:21:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.93,0:21:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙交給我來收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.36,0:22:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是葉嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.53,0:22:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.57,0:22:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把老大折磨成這樣\N我絕對不放過他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.97,0:22:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊\N清一下你多日來的積怨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.04,0:22:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吳東來，去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.95,0:22:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.85,0:22:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.32,0:22:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是怎麼了？\N吳竟然可以快速移動…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.06,0:22:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇到了吧，其實我可以行走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.33,0:22:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見識一下我這個秘密武器吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.77,0:22:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他竟然暗藏了這招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.67,0:22:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也太神奇了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.54,0:22:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個發明可以讓我的動作\N快到連眼睛都跟不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.84,0:22:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的人是你們啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.18,0:22:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳，怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.75,0:22:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閻王你說話啊\N我的動作快到你看不見吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.05,0:22:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是敢戳我的穴道\N我馬上就剁掉你的手指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.39,0:23:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣，怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.09,0:23:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戳得到穴道就來戳看看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.97,0:23:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了，這樣的話\N腳上的機關就用不到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.38,0:23:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手，不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.98,0:23:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對秘孔有意見的話就衝着我來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.29,0:23:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你連被點穴的價值都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.86,0:23:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吳東來…不，炸海獅完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.23,0:23:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說傻話了，這種菜沒人想吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.74,0:23:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想念你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.24,0:23:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了，朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.39,0:24:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂靜安眠的城市中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.66,0:24:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不禁陷入深深沉思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.66,0:24:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有許多瑣碎的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.57,0:24:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻沒錯過妳瞬間的不安神情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.37,0:24:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問妳是不是已經不再愛我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.44,0:24:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有答案就等於是答案了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.92,0:24:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在那種時候與妳相遇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.86,0:24:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會像被冰凍一般無法言語吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.76,0:24:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.47,0:24:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心跳好比四散的蝴蝶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.20,0:24:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成微風與色彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.41,0:25:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心跳爆裂飛散出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.28,0:25:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有如蝴蝶從我心中遠去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.92,0:25:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有妳 我的一切都將停擺
